metadata.name: Sweet Electric Chair
metadata.description:
When you’ve explored your own demons and you’ve accepted the beauty of your own suffering, you can begin to use the electric chair in your heart as a throne that embraces your true self.
You’ll become aware that to love is to suffer and to suffer is to grow, becoming addicted to the endorphins of happiness then you’ll realize that when you’re not in your comfort zone, finally you’ve begun to live.
